    "name": "Roblox Titanic Classic",
    "roblox_url": "https://www.roblox.com/games/4458424",
    "description": "Play the modern Roblox Titanic\r\nhttps://www.roblox.com/games/294790062/Roblox-Titanic\r\n\r\nThis game ran its course August 2009 to December 2015. \r\nThanks to everyone who played it.  Roblox was just in its infancy and this game has grown along with Roblox.  It was made without a security feature, due to being built before that feature even existed, and Roblox has made it mandatory as of July 2018.\r\n\r\nYou can actually get to a barebones version of this game by playing Roblox Titanic 2.0 (link above) and finding the option in the lobby gallery hallway.  You will see an option to play Roblox Titanic Classic.  It will not be the same, but you can explore the ship and experience the sinking.\r\n  \r\n",
